window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>I never thought I'd auction my v-card to survive.</b></p> <p>Now, I'm snowed in with three mountain men who want more than my innocence.</p> <p>The underground auction was my escape plan. Instead, it brought me face-to-face with three rugged brothers whose eyes see right through me and whose hands leave me trembling.</p> <p>Two months in their remote cabin was meant to be simple. Fulfill their terms, take the money, and start over. But I didn't expect <i>them</i>.</p> <p>Lucas is dark and intense, a leader whose control leaves me breathless—and wanting more. Bryce is playful and warm, but his charm hides a dangerous edge. Owen is quiet yet fiercely protective, his gaze stripping me bare in ways I can't resist.</p> <p>As obligation turns to desire, these men claim more than my heart and body. They want all of me.</p> <p>But when my past resurfaces, threatening everything, will they still stand by me? Or will my secrets shatter everything we've built?</p>"; 
